                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Familiar Form, Electric Function</span></p>
                <p>The overall silhouette is to remain largely unchanged, maintaining the lightweight underbone chassis that makes the XL so maneuverable. However, crucial design tweaks will mark its electric shift.</p>
